# AUDIO::FORCE_MUSIC_TRACK_LIST

## Summary
Forces the chosen station to play the given music track list. All other music track lists will be locked

## Parameters
* **STRING** radioStationName
* **STRING** trackListName
* **INT** timeOffsetMs

## Description
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Changes start time of a tracklist (milliseconds)
R* uses a random int: MISC::GET_RANDOM_INT_IN_RANGE(0, 13) * 60000)
